destination is almeria a southwestern spanish port roughly 310 
miles east of huelva 
the ships joyful sendoff friday coincided with the 498th 
anniversary of the day columbus began his first voyage to what 
would become known as america 
spain which bankrolled columbus spent 2 million to build the 
three ships from galician pine and oak from the pyrenees 
the ships were built to help promote the expo 92 worlds fair 
in the southern city of seville and to commemorate the 500th 
anniversary of columbus legendary voyage 
expo 92 is expected to attract 20 million visitors to seville 
from april to october 1992 
while the sailors will attempt to follow the exact sailing 
methods of columbus and his intrepid men the ships are equipped 
with sophisticated equipment to navigate via satellite and carry 
modernday lighting 
