a magazine alleged saturday that 
dozens of west german companies have helped iraq build rockets and 
chemical weapons and assisted baghdad acquire military nuclear 
technology 
according to hamburgbased der spiegel more than 100 west 
german companies are suspected of having helped iraq build its 
