for usjapanese relations 
it seemed to me that his indications were very positive 
damato said and i told him to stop this business of waiting to 
see what the world community does 
damato said he told kimura the japanese should understand that 
iraqs occupation of kuwait presents a window of opportunity 
for tokyo to demonstrate its willingness to cooperate with the 
united states as an ally on difficult national security questions 
